                        <h1>September 16, 2009</h1>                                  
                        CES is about double-digit days away, and the deadline for free registration is excitedly tapping on your shoulder. Don’t miss your chance to save big. <A href="/register">Register for the 2010 CES by October 1</A> to keep up to $200 from flying out of your pocket. And in the meantime, see a newly announced speaker that has global appeal and find out other ways to be kind to your budget as you gear up for the world’s largest consumer technology tradeshow coming to Las Vegas on January 7.

