<a name="3363"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">What’s in Store for the CE Industry this Holiday Season?</div>
<br />
<IMG border=0 hspace=6 vspace=4 align=right src="/print/images/content/CEA.gif" width=150 height=53>After a difficult year, industry hopes are pinned on the important holiday selling season to restore growth and salvage revenues. Yet, as the economy recovers, consumer spending remains in question. Will this holiday season be a harbinger of prosperity to come?<BR><BR>Attend the “2009 Holiday Sales and Forecast” session at CEA’s Industry Forum, Monday, October 19 at the Arizona Grand Resort in Phoenix, AZ to find out. <A href="http://www.ce.org/events/default.asp?siteUrl= http://speaker.ce.org/index.cfm?do=cus.eventSchedule|style=0|meetingID=1123|meetingContentType=meetingSchedule" target=_blank>View the full Industry Forum conference schedule</A>&nbsp;and <A href="http://www.ce.org/events/default.asp?siteUrl=http://speaker.ce.org/index.cfm?do=cus.meeting|meetingID=1123|style=0|meetingContentType=registration" target=_blank>register today.</A>

