<a name="3360"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Early Bird Gets the…Reduced Hotel Rate</div>
<br />
<IMG height=125 hspace=5 src="/print/images/photos/Strip_165x125.jpg" width=165 align=right border=0>Several CES hotels are now offering early bird and reduced rates for CES attendees.&nbsp; Take a look at some of the most recent money-saving announcements, and <A href="/print/hotelTravel/hotel.asp">check the complete list of official CES hotels</A>. Remember: The sooner you reserve a room, the better chance you have at saving money. Note: All listed rate changes are retroactive for existing reservations. <BR>
<UL class=text>
<LI class=text>ARIA at CityCenter is offering an early bird rate of $159 January 6 and $259 January 7-8</LI>
<LI class=text>Mirage peak rates start at $95/$205 (was $125/$225)</LI>
<LI class=text>The peak rate at Trump International is now $209 for a studio suite (was $249)</LI>
<LI class=text>Vdara at CityCenter is offering an early bird rate on all nights. Rates start at $114, plus $15 resort fee</LI>
<LI class=text>The Venetian has lowered their peak rate from $289 to $259 and introduced an off-peak rate of $159 for the night of January 10<BR></LI></UL>

