<a name="3359"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">Designers, Installers and Integrators Gear up for EHX@CES</div>
<br />
<A href="/print/news/upToTheMinute/ehx.asp"><IMG border=0 hspace=6 align=right src="/print/images/content/ehxatces.gif" width=200 height=54></A>New for 2010, <A href="/print/news/upToTheMinute/ehx.asp">EHX@CES</A> is powered by CE Pro to bring the EHX experience of a dedicated custom electronic exhibition to CES. Far more than a TechZone, <A href="/print/news/upToTheMinute/ehx.asp">EHX@CES</A> will offer unmatched industry knowledge at the CE Pro Headquarters located directly on the show floor. Gain insight from expert editors, attend can’t-miss training sessions, and participate in an exclusive meet-and-greet with industry leading writers and analysts, all taking place at CE Pro HQ! Access to the CE Pro Headquarters is included in all registration packages.<BR><BR><A href="/print/news/upToTheMinute/ehx.asp">EHX@CES</A> features custom and consumer electronics products and services for designers, installers and integrators who service the residential and commercial markets. The co-location of EHX and CES provides both exhibitors and attendees a value-packed destination to showcase and explore emerging trends and solutions in the custom electronics industry.<BR><BR><STRONG>Exhibit space is still available.</STRONG> Contact George Keegan at 508-663-1500 x229 or <A href="mailto:gkeegan@ehpub.com">gkeegan@ehpub.com</A>.

        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
        <img height="15" alt="" src="/print/images/framework/divider-line-long.gif"/><br />

<a name="3358"></a>
<div class="sub-content-header">How to Become a CES Exhibitor</div>
<br />
<IMG height=125 hspace=5 src="/print/images/photos/p13.jpg" width=165 align=right>You know CES is the place to see the best assortment of the newest technologies. You, too, can showcase your products and services at the International CES. If your company is a manufacturer/retailer of Mac-related products or is in the business of green products and services or applications and software then CES is the place for you.&nbsp; <A href="/print/exhibitors/space/default.asp">Exhibit today!</A> Open booth and meeting room space is still available. <A href="mailto:exhibit@CESweb.org">Please contact a CES representative</A> to find about these and other opportunities at CES.

        <img width="1" height="30" src="/print/images/framework/spacer.gif"/>
